1. Add Domain Value Validations
	Add more sophisticated email validation in Email value object
	Enhance password strength validation in Password value object
	Add URL validation for profile websites and media paths

2. Optimize Constants and Enums
	Move business rule constants into respective value objects where appropriate
	Add more descriptive enum values if needed
	Consider using enum extensions for display names

3. Add Comprehensive Domain Events
	Add events for likes, unlikes, profile updates, media uploads
	Add events for moderation actions and reports
	Ensure all significant domain operations raise appropriate events

4. File Structure Improvements
	Create Domain/Specifications/ folder for specification pattern
	Create Domain/Services/Models/ for service-specific DTOs like ModerationResult
	Consider splitting large entities into partial classes if they grow significantly